Fulcrum makes significant use of the following:
1. django-piston (https://bitbucket.org/jespern/django-piston)
2. django-model-schemas (https://bitbucket.org/eegg/django-model-schemas)

Basic usage
1. Get the latest version (https://github.com/octothorp/django-fulcrum)
2. Add fulcrum to installed apps
3. Include fulcrum in your url conf
4. Register a model with fulcrum
